		<title>08Entertainment And Crafts</title>
		<content>   There is no organised entertainment 
 in the village but local groups and   
 clubs hire the Vernon Institute or    
 Methodist Hall to hold social and     
 fund raising events i.e  barn         
 dances,discos,coffee mornings and     
 evenings,bingo sessions ,fashion shows
 ,etc.                                 
                                       
   There is a flourishing gardening    
 club which holds competitions and     
 shows during the year.their meetings  
 are held at the Vernon Institute.     
 In the village there is also a        
 qualified pianist who gives piano     
 lessons.                              
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
